trans-unit.source: Supplies a hash code for an object, using a hashing algorithm that ignores the case of strings.
trans-unit.target: Leverer en hash-kode for et objekt som bruker en nummeralgoritme som ignorerer bokstavtypen strenger.

trans-unit.source: CaseInsensitiveHashCodeProvider implements the <xref:System.Collections.IHashCodeProvider> interface supporting case-insensitive comparisons on strings, just as <xref:System.Collections.CaseInsensitiveComparer> implements the <xref:System.Collections.IComparer> interface supporting case-insensitive comparisons on strings.
trans-unit.target: CaseInsensitiveHashCodeProvider implementerer den <xref:System.Collections.IHashCodeProvider>grensesnittet støtter sammenligning av strenger, like <xref:System.Collections.CaseInsensitiveComparer>implementerer den <xref:System.Collections.IComparer>grensesnittet støtter sammenligninger i strenger.</xref:System.Collections.IComparer> </xref:System.Collections.CaseInsensitiveComparer> </xref:System.Collections.IHashCodeProvider>

trans-unit.source: The objects used as keys by a <xref:System.Collections.Hashtable> are required to override the <xref:System.Object.GetHashCode%2A?displayProperty=fullName> method (or the <xref:System.Collections.IHashCodeProvider> interface) and the <xref:System.Object.Equals%2A?displayProperty=fullName> method (or the <xref:System.Collections.IComparer> interface).
trans-unit.target: Objekter som brukes som nøkler av en <xref:System.Collections.Hashtable>kreves for å overstyre den <xref:System.Object.GetHashCode%2A?displayProperty=fullName>metoden (eller <xref:System.Collections.IHashCodeProvider>grensesnittet) og <xref:System.Object.Equals%2A?displayProperty=fullName>metoden (eller <xref:System.Collections.IComparer>grensesnittet).</xref:System.Collections.IComparer> </xref:System.Object.Equals%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Collections.IHashCodeProvider> </xref:System.Object.GetHashCode%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Collections.Hashtable>

trans-unit.source: The implementation of both methods or interfaces must handle case sensitivity the same way; otherwise, the <xref:System.Collections.Hashtable> might behave incorrectly.
trans-unit.target: Implementeringen av både metoder eller grensesnitt må behandle store og små bokstaver på samme måte; Hvis ikke, den <xref:System.Collections.Hashtable>fungerer på feil måte.</xref:System.Collections.Hashtable>

trans-unit.source: For example, when creating a <xref:System.Collections.Hashtable>, you must use this class with the <xref:System.Collections.CaseInsensitiveComparer> class or any case-insensitive <xref:System.Collections.IComparer> implementation.
trans-unit.target: For eksempel når du oppretter en <xref:System.Collections.Hashtable>, må du bruke denne klassen med den <xref:System.Collections.CaseInsensitiveComparer>klasse eller en samlingstype <xref:System.Collections.IComparer>implementering.</xref:System.Collections.IComparer> </xref:System.Collections.CaseInsensitiveComparer> </xref:System.Collections.Hashtable>

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Collections.CaseInsensitiveHashCodeProvider"></xref> class using the <xref:System.Threading.Thread.CurrentCulture%2A?displayProperty=fullName> of the current thread.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.Collections.CaseInsensitiveHashCodeProvider"> </xref> klasse ved hjelp av den <xref:System.Threading.Thread.CurrentCulture%2A?displayProperty=fullName> for gjeldende tråd.

trans-unit.source: When the <xref:System.Collections.CaseInsensitiveHashCodeProvider> instance is created using this constructor, the <xref:System.Threading.Thread.CurrentCulture%2A?displayProperty=fullName> of the current thread is saved.
trans-unit.target: Når den <xref:System.Collections.CaseInsensitiveHashCodeProvider>forekomst opprettes med denne konstruktøren av <xref:System.Threading.Thread.CurrentCulture%2A?displayProperty=fullName>for gjeldende tråd er lagret.</xref:System.Threading.Thread.CurrentCulture%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Collections.CaseInsensitiveHashCodeProvider>

trans-unit.source: Comparison procedures use the saved culture to determine the casing rules; therefore, hash code comparisons might have different results depending on the culture.
trans-unit.target: Sammenligning prosedyrer Bruk den lagrede kulturen til å fastslå små og reglene. hash-kode sammenligninger kan derfor ha forskjellige resultater, alt etter kulturen.

trans-unit.source: For more information on culture-specific comparisons, see the <xref:System.Globalization> namespace and [Globalization and Localization](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).
trans-unit.target: For mer informasjon om kultur-spesifikke sammenligninger, kan du se den <xref:System.Globalization>navneområde og [globalisering og lokalisering](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).</xref:System.Globalization>

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Collections.CaseInsensitiveHashCodeProvider"></xref> class using the specified <xref:System.Globalization.CultureInfo?displayProperty=fullName>.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.Collections.CaseInsensitiveHashCodeProvider"> </xref> klasse parametersettet med de angitte <xref:System.Globalization.CultureInfo?displayProperty=fullName>.

trans-unit.source: Comparison procedures use the specified <xref:System.Globalization.CultureInfo?displayProperty=fullName> to determine the casing rules.
trans-unit.target: Sammenligning prosedyrer bruke den angitte <xref:System.Globalization.CultureInfo?displayProperty=fullName>å finne ut av små og-regler.</xref:System.Globalization.CultureInfo?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: Returns a hash code for the given object, using a hashing algorithm that ignores the case of strings.
trans-unit.target: Returnerer en hash-kode for det angitte objektet, ved hjelp av en nummeralgoritme som ignorerer bokstavtypen strenger.

trans-unit.source: The return value from this method must not be persisted for two reasons.
trans-unit.target: Verdien som returneres fra denne metoden må ikke gjøres fast to grunner.

trans-unit.source: First, the hash function of a class might be altered to generate a better distribution, thereby rendering any values from the old hash function useless.
trans-unit.target: Hash-funksjonen av en klasse kan først endres for å generere en bedre distribusjon, og dermed gjengivelse av alle verdier fra den gamle hash-funksjonen ubrukelige.

trans-unit.source: Second, the default implementation of this class does not guarantee that the same value will be returned by different instances.
trans-unit.target: Sekundet, standard implementering av denne klassen ikke garantere at den samme verdien, returneres av forskjellige forekomster.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Object> for which a hash code is to be returned.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Object>for som en hash-kode er som skal returneres.</xref:System.Object>
